- switch the repo's analysis options to using package:lints

This updates the analysis options files for this repo to bring in the recommended set of lints from `package:lints`. The commits here build on the work in https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/pull/5520; after that lands I'll re-sync this branch and squash the commits.
